ivardefs.name: actor
ivardefs.desc: The device, practitioner, etc. who performed the action.  It should be assumed that the actor is the dispenser of the medication.

ivardefs.name: onBehalfOf
ivardefs.desc: The organization the device or practitioner was acting on behalf of.

properties.desc: Indicates who or what performed the event.  It should be assumed that the performer is the dispenser of the medication.
